<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>An Evening with Chance Stanley</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;600;700&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
}

html{
scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{

font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;
background:#f5f0e3;
color:#2e241b;
line-height:1.6;

}

.hero{

height:100vh;

background:
linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.45),rgba(0,0,0,.45)),
url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500530855697-b586d89ba3ee?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1800&q=80");

background-size:cover;
background-position:center;

display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;

text-align:center;

padding:30px;

color:white;

}

.hero-inner{

max-width:850px;

backdrop-filter:blur(2px);

}

.hero h1{

font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;

font-size:4rem;

margin-bottom:10px;

letter-spacing:1px;

}

.hero h2{

font-weight:300;

font-size:1.6rem;

margin-bottom:30px;

color:#f3d48a;

}

.hero p{

font-size:1.2rem;

margin-bottom:18px;

}

.scroll{

margin-top:40px;

font-size:1rem;

opacity:.9;

animation:bounce 2s infinite;

}

@keyframes bounce{

0%,100%{transform:translateY(0);}
50%{transform:translateY(10px);}

}

.container{

max-width:900px;

margin:auto;

padding:50px 20px;

}

.card{

background:white;

border-radius:18px;

padding:35px;

box-shadow:0 10px 35px rgba(0,0,0,.12);

margin-top:-80px;

position:relative;

z-index:2;

}

.section-title{

font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;

font-size:2.3rem;

margin-bottom:20px;

text-align:center;

}

.intro{

font-size:1.1rem;

text-align:center;

margin-bottom:30px;

}

label{

display:block;

margin-top:20px;

font-weight:600;

}

input,
textarea,
select{

width:100%;

padding:14px;

margin-top:8px;

border-radius:12px;

border:1px solid #d5c9b7;

font-size:16px;

font-family:inherit;

background:#fffdf8;

}

textarea{

min-height:110px;

resize:vertical;

}

.button{

margin-top:35px;

width:100%;

padding:18px;

background:#87613d;

color:white;

border:none;

border-radius:14px;

font-size:20px;

font-weight:bold;

cursor:pointer;

transition:.3s;

}

.button:hover{

background:#6e4c2f;

transform:translateY(-2px);

}

.result{

display:none;

margin-top:35px;

padding:30px;

background:#eef6ea;

border-radius:16px;

}

.result h2{

font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;

font-size:2rem;

margin-bottom:15px;

}.result p{

font-size:1.15rem;

margin:10px 0;

}

.price{

font-size:2rem;

font-weight:bold;

color:#6b4b2c;

margin:15px 0;

}

.includes{

margin-top:45px;

}

.includes ul{

margin-top:20px;

padding-left:25px;

}

.includes li{

margin-bottom:14px;

font-size:1.08rem;

}

.contact{

margin-top:45px;

text-align:center;

}

.contact a{

display:inline-block;

margin:10px;

padding:14px 26px;

background:#87613d;

color:white;

text-decoration:none;

border-radius:12px;

font-weight:bold;

transition:.3s;

}

.contact a:hover{

background:#6e4c2f;

}

.footer-quote{

margin-top:55px;

text-align:center;

font-style:italic;

font-size:1.15rem;

color:#5b5145;

}

@media(max-width:768px){

.hero h1{

font-size:2.8rem;

}

.hero h2{

font-size:1.2rem;

}

.card{

margin-top:-40px;

padding:24px;

}

.section-title{

font-size:1.9rem;

}

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-inner">

<h1>An Evening with Chance Stanley</h1>

<h2>Bring Live Music Home</h2>

<p>After years of chasing songs down two-lane highways and little towns across America, I'd love to bring that same experience to your home.</p>

<p>You bring the people.<br>
I'll bring the songs, the stories, and everything needed for an unforgettable evening.</p>

<p><strong>If you've got the people, I've got the songs.<br>Let's see if we can make it happen.</strong></p>

<div class="scroll">

⬇ Scroll to Begin ⬇

</div>

</div>

</section>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">

<h2 class="section-title">

Tell Me About Your Event

</h2>

<p class="intro">

Whether it's a birthday, anniversary, backyard gathering, fundraiser, neighborhood get-together, or simply a room full of good people...I'd be honored to bring live music to your corner of the world.

</p>

<label>🏡 Host City</label>

<input
id="city"
placeholder="Example: Nashville">

<label>🌎 State</label>

<select id="state">

<option>Mississippi</option>

<option>Alabama</option>

<option>Tennessee</option>

<option>Arkansas</option>

<option>Louisiana</option>

<option>Georgia</option>

<option>Kentucky</option>

<option>Other</option>

</select>

<label>📅 Preferred Dates</label>

<textarea
id="dates"
placeholder="One date, several dates, or simply 'Flexible'"></textarea>

<label>👥 Estimated Guests (Optional)</label>

<input
id="guests"
placeholder="Example: 40">

<button
class="button"
onclick="estimate()">

🚗 See If We Can Make It Happen

</button>

<div
id="result"
class="result">

</div><div class="includes">

<h2 class="section-title">

Every House Concert Includes

</h2>

<ul>

<li>🎸 90–120 minute live performance tailored to your event</li>

<li>🎶 Original music, some of your favorite classics, and the stories behind the songs</li>

<li>🔊 Professional PA system and sound equipment</li>

<li>🪑 Complete setup and teardown</li>

<li>🤝 Personal planning before your event</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="contact">

<h2 class="section-title">

Ready To Talk Dates?

</h2>

<p>

Once you have a few dates in mind, reach out and we’ll see what works for everyone.

</p>

<a href="tel:6627200678">

📞 Call / Text Chance

</a>

<a href="mailto:chance_stanley@aol.com">

✉️ Email Chance

</a>

</div>

<p class="footer-quote">

“Every road has a story. I’d be honored to bring a few of mine to your home.”

<br>

— Chance Stanley

</p>

</div>

</div>

<script>

function estimate(){

const city=document.getElementById("city").value.trim();

const state=document.getElementById("state").value;

const dates=document.getElementById("dates").value.trim();

const guests=document.getElementById("guests").value.trim();

if(!city){

alert("Add the host city first.");

return;

}

const farCities=[
"chicago",
"denver",
"phoenix",
"miami",
"orlando",
"new york",
"boston",
"los angeles",
"seattle",
"las vegas",
"minneapolis",
"detroit",
"philadelphia",
"washington",
"baltimore"
];

const locationText=(city+" "+state).toLowerCase();

const extended=farCities.some(function(place){

return locationText.includes(place);

});

const result=document.getElementById("result");

let options="";

if(extended){

options=`

<h2>I’d Love To Come Your Way</h2>

<p>Your event looks like it may fall into my extended touring range.</p>

<p class="price">$800 All-Inclusive</p>

<p>or</p>

<p class="price">$700 + One Night of Lodging</p>

`;

}else{

options=`

<h2>I’d Love To Come Your Way</h2>

<p>Your event looks like it may fit my standard house concert range.</p>

<p class="price">$600 All-Inclusive</p>

<p>or</p>

<p class="price">$500 + One Night of Lodging</p>

`;

}

let details=`

<p><strong>Host Location:</strong> ${city}, ${state}</p>

`;

if(dates){

details+=`

<p><strong>Preferred Dates:</strong> ${dates}</p>

`;

}

if(guests){

details+=`

<p><strong>Estimated Guests:</strong> ${guests}</p>

`;

}

result.innerHTML=options+details+`

<p>This is an estimate only. Dates are not reserved until confirmed directly with Chance.</p>

`;

result.style.display="block";

result.scrollIntoView({behavior:"smooth",block:"start"});

}

</script></body>

</html>